  "What does 'linearity of integration' mean?": "“融合的线性”意味着什么?",
  "The integral is always a straight line": "整体体始终是一条直线",
  "Integration only works on linear functions": "整合仅对线性函数有效",
  "The integral of a sum equals the sum of the integrals, and constants can be pulled out of the integral": "整数的整数等于整数的和,常数可以从整数中提取出来。",
  "All integrals produce linear functions": "所有整体体都产生线性函数",
  "Linearity means: integral of [af(x) + bg(x)] dx = a * integral of f(x) dx + b * integral of g(x) dx. This property allows us to integrate term by term and factor out constants.": "线性是指:[af(x)+bg(x)] dx = * f(x) dx + b * 的有机体的有机体。此属性允许我们按术语和因数组合术语并排除常数。",
  "What does 'direction change' mean for a particle in rectilinear motion?": "直线运动中的粒子的“方向改变”意味着什么?",
  "The acceleration is zero": "加速度为零,加速度为零",
  "The position function has a point of inflection": "位置函数有一个反射点",
  "The particle reaches its maximum speed": "粒子达到最大速度",
  "The velocity changes sign, meaning the particle reverses its motion": "速度变化符号 意思是粒子反转其运动",
  "A direction change occurs when the velocity changes sign (passes through zero and changes from positive to negative or vice versa). At a direction change, the position function has a local extremum. The particle reverses its motion at that instant.": "当速度改变符号时,即发生方向变化(通过零,从正向负向负或反向变化)。在方向变化时,位置函数有一个局部的极限。当时粒子会反转其运动。",
  "What does 'antiderivative' mean?": "\"异想天开\"是什么意思?",
  "A function F(x) whose derivative equals f(x), i.e., F'(x) = f(x)": "F(x) 函数 F(x) ,其衍生函数等于 f(x),即 F'(x) = f(x)",
  "The second derivative of a function": "函数的第二个衍生物",
  "The negative of the derivative": "衍生物的负值",
  "The reciprocal of the derivative": "衍生物对等对等",
  "An antiderivative of f(x) is a function F(x) such that F'(x) = f(x). If F is one antiderivative, then F + C (for any constant C) is also an antiderivative. The process of finding antiderivatives is called indefinite integration.": "f(x) 的抗衍生物是一种F(x) 函数, 即 F'(x) = f(x) 。 如果 F 是 一种抗衍生物, 那么F + C (对于任何恒定的 C) 也是一种抗衍生物。 找到抗衍生物的过程被称为无限期融合 。",
  "What does 'total change' differ from 'net change'?": "“ 全部变化” 与“ 净变化” 有何不同 ?",
  "Total change is always smaller than net change under most circumstances involving change": "在大多数涉及变化的情况下,总变化总变化总是小于净变化",
  "Total change sums all increases and decreases separately (using absolute values); net change is the final value minus the initial value": "全部变化合计所有增减(使用绝对值);净变化是最终值减去初始值",
  "Net change uses absolute values; total change does not according to widely held views on this topic": "净变化使用绝对值;完全变化不根据对本专题广泛持有的看法",
  "They are the same thing, as most introductory frameworks would predict when analyzing change dynamics": "它们是一样的,正如大多数介绍性框架在分析变化动态时预测的那样",
  "Total change (or total variation) adds up all increases and all decreases without cancellation (analogous to total distance). Net change is F(b) - F(a), which allows increases and decreases to cancel (analogous to displacement). Total change >= |net change|.": "总变化(或总变差)加起来,所有增长和所有下降不取消(与总距离相当)。净变化是F(b)-F(a),允许增减取消(与变换一致)。",
  "What is the 'definite integral' of a function?": "函数的“ 无限整体性” 是什么?",
  "Any integral that has a definite answer": "任何有明确答案的有机体",
  "An integral without limits of integration": "一体化不受限制的组成部分",
  "An integral that always produces a positive number": "一个总能产生正数的有机体",
  "The signed area between the function and the x-axis over a specified interval [a, b], evaluated as F(b) - F(a)": "在指定间隔[a, b]内,函数与x轴之间在函数和x轴之间签署的区域,以F(b)-F(a)被评价为F(b)-F(a)",
  "A definite integral has specified upper and lower limits [a, b] and evaluates to a number: integral from a to b of f(x) dx = F(b) - F(a). It represents the net signed area between the curve and the x-axis.": "确定的整体体指定了上限和下限[a、b],并对数字进行了评价:从 f(x) dx = F(b) - F(a)的a至b的有机体。它代表曲线和x轴之间的净签名区域。",
  "What does 'speed' mean compared to 'velocity'?": "与“速度”相比,“速度”意味着什么?",
  "They are the same thing": "它们是同一回事",
  "Speed is the absolute value of velocity; it measures how fast without regard to direction": "速度是速度的绝对值;它测量速度,而不考虑方向",
  "Speed is the derivative of velocity": "速度是速度的衍生物",
  "Velocity is always positive; speed can be negative": "速度总是正速;速度可能是负速",
  "Speed = |v(t)| is the magnitude of velocity. Velocity is a signed quantity (positive for forward, negative for backward), while speed is always non-negative. Integrating speed gives total distance; integrating velocity gives net displacement.": "速度 = v(t)  是速度的大小。 速度是一个签名数量( 前向正数, 后向负数) , 而速度总是非负数 。 集成速度表示总距离; 集成速度表示净置换 。",
  "What does 'initial condition' mean for an accumulation problem?": "对于积累问题,“初始条件”意味着什么?",
  "The condition that the function equals zero": "函数等于 0 的条件",
  "The known value of the quantity at the starting time, used to determine the particular solution": "用于确定特定解决方案的起始时间已知数量值",
  "The maximum value of the function": "函数的最大值",
  "The derivative at time zero": "时间为零的衍生物",
  "An initial condition specifies the value of the quantity at a given starting time (e.g., F(0) = 5). Combined with the rate of change F'(t), it allows us to find the quantity at any time: F(t) = F(0) + integral from 0 to t of F'(s) ds.": "初始条件指定了特定起始时间的数量值(如F(0) = 5) , 加上F(t) 的变动率, 使我们可以随时找到数量: F(t) = F(0) + F(s) ds 从0到 t的有机体。",
  "What is 'marginal analysis' in economics?": "经济学中“边际分析”是什么?",
  "Analyzing the margins of a page": "分析页面边距",
  "Using derivatives and integrals to analyze the cost, revenue, or profit of producing one additional unit": "利用衍生物和集成物分析生产一个额外单位的成本、收入或利润",
  "Finding the total cost of all production": "查明所有生产的总成本",
  "Computing the profit margin as a percentage": "以百分比计算利润率",
  "Marginal analysis uses calculus to study incremental changes. The marginal cost C'(x), marginal revenue R'(x), and marginal profit P'(x) are derivatives that represent per-unit rates. Integrating these marginals gives total changes in cost, revenue, or profit.": "边际分析利用计算法来研究递增变化。边际成本 C''(x),边际收入 R'(x)和边际利润 P'(x)是代表单位利率的衍生物。 将这些边际因素结合起来,就会在成本、收入或利润方面发生全面变化。",
  "What does the 'chain rule with FTC' mean?": "“与公平贸易委员会一起的链条规则”是什么意思?",
  "The chain rule replaces the FTC": "链规则取代公平贸易委员会",
  "FTC applies only when the upper limit is x": "公平贸易委员会只在上限为x时适用",
  "When differentiating g(x) = integral from a to h(x) of f(t) dt, the result is g'(x) = f(h(x)) * h'(x)": "当区分 g( x) = f( t) dt 从 a 到 h( x) 的 等于 等于 f( h) = f( h( x) ) * h' (x) 时,结果为 g' ( x) = f( h) = h' (x) * h' (x)",
  "The chain rule has no connection to FTC": "连锁规则与公平贸易委员会没有任何联系",
  "When the upper limit of integration is a function h(x) rather than just x, the chain rule combines with FTC Part 1: d/dx [integral from a to h(x) of f(t) dt] = f(h(x)) * h'(x). The extra factor h'(x) comes from the chain rule.": "当整合的上限是函数h(x)而不是仅仅x时,链规则与FTC Part 1:d/dx(从f(t)dt的a到h(x)的整数)=f(h(x))* h'(x)。额外系数h'(x)来自链规则。",
  "What does 'equilibrium quantity' mean in supply and demand?": "“平衡数量”在供求方面意味着什么?",
  "The maximum quantity a supplier can produce": "供应商能够生产的最大数量",
  "The average of supply and demand": "供求平均数",
  "The quantity where supply equals demand, resulting in no tendency for the price to change": "供应量等于需求量,导致价格没有变化趋势",
  "The quantity that minimizes cost": "最大限度减少费用的数量",
  "The equilibrium quantity is where the supply and demand curves intersect. At this point, the quantity supplied equals the quantity demanded, and the market price is stable. Consumer and producer surplus are calculated using integrals relative to this equilibrium point.": "平衡数量是供求曲线交错之处。 此时, 供应数量等于所需数量, 市场价格稳定。 消费者和生产者盈余是使用与这个平衡点相对应的组合计算出来的。",
  "A company's daily sales rate follows S(t) = 500 - 20t + t^2 units per day for a 10-day period. What are the total units sold?": "公司每天的销售率在10天的时期内低于S(t)=500 - 20t + t2单位的每日销售率。",
  "Approximately 5000 units": "约5000个单位",
  "Approximately 3667 units": "约3667个单位",
  "Approximately 4333 units": "约4333个单位",
  "Approximately 3000 units": "约3 000个单位",
  "Total = integral from 0 to 10 of (500 - 20t + t^2) dt = [500t - 10t^2 + t^3/3] from 0 to 10 = 5000 - 1000 + 1000/3 = 4000 + 333.3 = 4333.3 units (approximately 4333).": "共计=0至10(500-20t + t2) dt = 0至10= 5000-1000 + 1000/3 = 40000 + 333.3 = 4333.3 单位(约4333)",
  "A patient receives medication intravenously at rate R_in(t) = 20 mg/hr. The body metabolizes the drug at rate R_out(t) = 0.4*C(t) mg/hr, where C(t) is the current amount. If C(0) = 0 and after a long time the drug level approaches equilibrium, what is the equilibrium level?": "以R_in(t) = 20 mg/hr的速度静脉注射药物。身体代谢药物的速率是R_out(t) = 0.4*C(t) mg/hr,而C(t) 是当量。如果C(0) = 0 且药物水平长期接近平衡,那么平衡水平是多少?",
  "50 mg": "50毫克 50毫克",
  "20 mg": "20毫克 20毫克",
  "100 mg": "100 毫克",
  "80 mg": "80 毫克",
  "At equilibrium, R_in = R_out: 20 = 0.4*C, so C = 50 mg. The net rate dC/dt = 20 - 0.4C = 0 at equilibrium. This is the steady-state drug level.": "在平衡时,R_in=R_out:20=0.4*C,C=50毫克。净速率dC/dt=20 - 0.4C=0。这是稳定状态药物水平。",
  "A river's flow rate past a measuring station varies as Q(t) = 1000 + 500*sin(pi*t/6) cubic feet per second, where t is in hours. What is the total volume of water that flows past in 12 hours?": "河流流经测量站的流速因Q(t) = 1000+ 500*sin(pi*t/6) 立方英尺/秒而不同,以小时计。12小时内流过的水总量是多少?",
  "54,000,000 cubic feet": "54 000 000立方英尺",
  "43,200,000 cubic feet": "43 200 000立方英尺",
  "36,000,000 cubic feet": "36 000 000立方英尺",
  "21,600,000 cubic feet": "21 600 000立方英尺",
  "Volume = integral from 0 to 12 of Q(t) * 3600 dt (converting hours to seconds for the rate). Actually, since Q is in ft^3/s and t is in hours, we need: Volume = integral from 0 to 12 of Q(t) dt * 3600 s/hr. Integral of (1000 + 500sin(pi*t/6)) from 0 to 12 = [1000t - 500*(6/pi)*cos(pi*t/6)] from 0 to 12 = 12,000 - (3000/pi)(cos(2pi) - cos(0)) = 12,000 - 0 = 12,000 ft^3*hr. Converting: 12,000 * 3600 = 43,200,000 cubic feet.": "卷号 = Q(t) * 3600 dt 0 至 12 的有机体 = Q(t) * 3600 dt * 3600 s/hr。卷号 = Q(t) 0 至 12 的有机体 = 3600 dt * 3600 s/hr。卷号 = 1 000 + 500 sin (pi* et/6 ) 0 至 12 = 1000 - 500 * (6/pi) *cos (pi* 6)] = 0 = 12 000 - 3 000 /pi (cos (2pi) - cos (0) = 12 000 - 0 = 12 000 ft 3 shr。转换: 12 000 * 3600 = 43 200 000 立方英尺。",
  "A balloon is inflated so its volume increases at a rate V'(t) = 12t - t^2 cm^3/s. Starting from empty, what is the maximum volume the balloon reaches before it starts deflating?": "气球被膨胀, 以V'( t) = 12t - t2 cm3/ s 的速度增加气球的体积。 从空开始,气球在开始减缩之前达到的最大体积是多少?",
  "216 cm^3": "216厘米3",
  "432 cm^3": "432厘米3",
  "288 cm^3": "288厘米3",
  "144 cm^3": "144厘米3",
  "V'(t) = 0 when 12t - t^2 = 0, so t(12 - t) = 0, giving t = 12 (deflation starts). V(12) = integral from 0 to 12 of (12t - t^2) dt = [6t^2 - t^3/3] from 0 to 12 = 864 - 576 = 288 cm^3.": "V'(t) = 0 当 12t - t2 = 0, 所以 t( 12 - t) = 0, 给 t = 12( 通货膨胀开始)。 V( 12) = 0 至 12 dt = [6t2 - t3] = 0至 12 = 864 - 576 = 288 cm 3。",
  "A taxi charges at a rate of C'(d) = 2 + 0.5/(d+1) dollars per mile, where d is distance in miles. What is the total fare for a 4-mile ride if the base fare is $3?": "C'(d)=2+0.5/(d+1)每英里0.5/(d+1)美元的计程车费, d是英里的距离。如果基价是3美元,4英里的车程总票价是多少?",
  "3 + 8 + 0.5*ln(5) dollars": "3+8+8+0.5*00(5)美元",
  "11 dollars": "11美元",
  "3 + 8 dollars": "3+8美元",
  "3 + 4 + 0.5*ln(5) dollars": "3+4+4+0.5*00(5)美元",
  "Fare = 3 + integral from 0 to 4 of [2 + 0.5/(d+1)] dd = 3 + [2d + 0.5*ln(d+1)] from 0 to 4 = 3 + (8 + 0.5*ln(5)) - 0 = 3 + 8 + 0.5*ln(5) dollars, which is approximately $11.80.": "法尔=3+组成部分,0至4,[2+0.5/(d+1)] dd=3+[2d+0.5*ln(d+1)],0至4=3+3+3+3+(8+0.5*ln(5)) - 0=3+8+0.5*ln(5),约合11.80美元。",
  "A solar panel generates electricity at rate P(t) = 100*sin^2(pi*t/12) watts for 0 <= t <= 12 hours (daytime). The total energy generated in 12 hours is:": "太阳能电池板以P(t) = 100*sin§2(pi*t/12) watts的速度发电,时间为0  t  12小时(日间)。",
  "900 watt-hours": "900瓦小时",
  "600 watt-hours": "600瓦小时",
  "1200 watt-hours": "1200瓦小时",
  "300 watt-hours": "300瓦小时",
  "Using sin^2(u) = (1 - cos(2u))/2: integral from 0 to 12 of 100*(1 - cos(pi*t/6))/2 dt = 50 * integral of [1 - cos(pi*t/6)] dt from 0 to 12 = 50[t - (6/pi)*sin(pi*t/6)] from 0 to 12 = 50[12 - (6/pi)(sin(2pi) - sin(0))] = 50*12 = 600 watt-hours.": "使用sin%2(u) = 1 - cos( 2u) = 2: 100* (1 - cos(pi*t/6)) 2 dt = 50 * 中0 - cos(pi*t/6) dt 中0 - 12 = 50[t - (6/pi) *sin(pi*t/6)] 中0 - 12 = 50[12 - (6/pi) (sin(2pi) - 罪(0)] = 50 *12 = 600瓦小时。",
  "A pollution source releases contaminants into a lake at rate R(t) = 50*e^(-0.1t) kg/day. A filter removes contaminants at 20 kg/day. Starting with a clean lake, when does the contaminant level stop increasing?": "污染源将污染物以R(t) = 50*e(-0.1t) 千克/天的速度释放到湖中,过滤器将污染物在20千克/天消除。从清洁湖开始,污染物水平何时停止上升?",
  "At t = 10 days": "t t = 10天",
  "At t = 5 days": "t = 5天",
  "At t = 10*ln(2.5) days": "吨 = 10*ln(2.5)天",
  "The level never stops increasing": "水平从未停止上升",
  "Net rate = 50*e^(-0.1t) - 20. This equals zero when 50*e^(-0.1t) = 20, so e^(-0.1t) = 0.4, giving -0.1t = ln(0.4) = -ln(2.5). Therefore t = 10*ln(2.5) = approximately 9.16 days.": "净速率=50 * e(-0.1t) - 20. 当50 * (-0.1t) = 20, e(-0.1t) = 0.4, 给 -0.1t = In(0.4) = - ln(2.5) 时, 净速率等于零。 因此 t = 10 *ln(2.5) = 约9.16天。",
  "A cyclist's speed varies as v(t) = 15 - 3|t - 3| mph for 0 <= t <= 6 hours. What is the total distance traveled?": "自行车手的速度因 v(t) = 15 - 3t - 33mph = 0 _ t _ _ 6小时而不同。总距离是多少?",
  "63 miles": "63英里 63英里",
  "45 miles": "45英里45英里",
  "54 miles": "54英里",
  "90 miles": "90英里",
  "Since v(t) >= 0 for all t in [0, 6] (minimum is v(0) = v(6) = 6), total distance = integral from 0 to 6 of v(t) dt. Split at t = 3: integral from 0 to 3 of (15 - 3(3-t)) dt + integral from 3 to 6 of (15 - 3(t-3)) dt = integral from 0 to 3 of (6 + 3t) dt + integral from 3 to 6 of (24 - 3t) dt = [6t + 3t^2/2] from 0 to 3 + [24t - 3t^2/2] from 3 to 6 = (18 + 13.5) + (144 - 54 - 72 + 13.5) = 31.5 + 31.5 = 63 miles.": "从v(t)  0= 0,所有吨,[0,6] (最小值为 v(0) = v(6) = 6),总距离= v(t) dt的0-6, dt拆分t = 3: 0-3, dt + 3-6, (15 - 3(3)) dt + 3-6, dt + 3-6, (6 + 3, 3) dt + 3-6, (24 - 3) dt = [6t + 3, 2/2], 从0 + 3 + [24t - 3t2] 2, 从 3 = 6 + (18 + 13.5) + (144 - 54 - 72 + 13.5) = 31.5 + 31.5 + 31.5 = 63英里。",
  "An account earns interest and has withdrawals. The rate of change of the balance is B'(t) = 0.05*B(t) - 200 (in dollars per year). If B(0) = $10,000, is the account growing or shrinking initially?": "账户赚取利息并有提款。 余额的变动率是 B'(t) = 0.05* B(t) - 200 (以每年美元计)。 如果 B(0) = 10,000, 该账户最初是增长还是收缩?",
  "Cannot be determined without more information": "没有更多信息无法确定",
  "Constant, since interest and withdrawals balance": "由于利息和提款余额",
  "Shrinking, since withdrawals exceed interest": "正在减少,因为提款超过利息",
  "Growing, since B'(0) = 0.05(10,000) - 200 = 300 > 0": "自B'(0) = 0.05(10,000) - 200 = 300 > 0",
  "B'(0) = 0.05(10,000) - 200 = 500 - 200 = 300 > 0. The interest earned ($500/year) exceeds the withdrawal rate ($200/year), so the balance is initially growing at $300/year.": "B'(0) = 0.05(10,000) - 200 = 500 - 200 = 300 > 0。 所得利息(500美元/年)超过提款率(200美元/年),因此余额最初以每年300美元的速度增长。",
  "A dam controls water release. During a 10-hour flood event, inflow is R_in(t) = 500 + 100*sin(pi*t/5) ft^3/s and outflow is set to a constant 550 ft^3/s. What is the net change in reservoir volume over the 10 hours (in ft^3)?": "水坝控制水的释放。 在10小时的洪水事件中,R_in(t) = 500 + 100 *sin(pi*t/5) ft}3/s 和流出定在恒定值 550 ft}3/s。 10小时储油层量的净变化是多少(ft}3)?",
  "1,800,000 ft^3": "1 800 000英尺3",
